      "name": "Impair Defenses: Disable or Modify Tools",
      "description": "Custom AV killers (All.exe, Allpatch2.exe) terminate EDR/AV processes using ThrottleBlood.sys kernel driver. Global Defender exclusions set; real-time protection disabled; Defender cache and prefetch cleaned.",
